# SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only
config VMBOX
    tristate "QEMU virtual mailbox character device"
    depends on OF
    help
      Build the vmbox platform character driver for the QEMU-emulated
      virt,mbox MMIO mailbox device. The driver exposes /dev/vmbox0 and is
      intended for testing MMIO, IRQ, poll, ioctl, and debugfs driver paths.
